The paper proposes a novel subspace clustering model that improves upon existing methods by explicitly characterizing certain properties of the reconstruction matrix using latent cluster indicators. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
